<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1036113>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Almafuerte peripampasica sp. nov., female (MACN-Ar 30442). a, left chelicera, apical view; b, same, posterior view, c, same, detail of cheliceral fang and tooth; d, detail of venom outlet; e, left palp, retrolateral view; f, detail of dorsal cuticle of palpal tibia, showing the row of trichobothria; g, detail of trichobothrial socket; h, tarsal claw, prolateral view; i, detail of tarsal chemosensory seta." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1036113/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1036121>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Almafuerte peripampasica sp. nov., male (MACN-Ar 30443). a, left palp, ventral view; b, same, closer view of the copulatory bulb, c, same, detail of embolus tip; d, left palp, retrolateral view; e, same, closer view of RTA; f, retrolateral tegular process (RTP), ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1036121/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1036119>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Almafuerte peripampasica sp. nov., female (MACN-Ar 30442). a, epigynum, ventral view; b, same, detail of copulatory openings, c, same, detail of anterior hood; d, vulva, dorsal view; e, same, closer view; f, same, detail of the left secondary spermathecae." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1036119/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1036111>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Almafuerte peripampasica sp. nov., female (MACN-Ar 30442). a, carapace, dorsal view; b, detail of ocular region, c, cephalothorax, ventral view; d, mouthparts, ventral view; e, feathery scales on carapace surface." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1036111/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

